               </ui>
               <value>
                  <text xliff:rid="F283359A-CB63-4833-A5C9-F9B1682150CA">TERMS AND CONDITIONS : 1) Our responsibility ceases on delivery of goods to Transporter / as per individual P.O. 2)No Claim will be entertained if not lodged within two weeks from the date of our invoice . 3) All transactions and bills are subject to Pune Jurisdication. 4) Interest @ 24% will be charged extra if not paid within agreed period.</text>
               </value>
